  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 1
  Paragraph: 12
Title: Free And Easy Wandering
---
Therefore I say, the Perfect Man has no self; the Holy Man has no
merit; the Sage has no fame.
